    - "Growing stronger, not growing fat"
    - "It's not an adventure until something goes wrong"
    - "Study the juvenile delinquent"
    - "We're in business to save our home planet"
    - "The best product is the one you don't have to replace"

when_to_consult:
  - "Feeling pressure to scale or grow when your gut says to stay small and stay good"
  - "Struggling with the tension between profit and purpose — wondering if you have to choose"
  - "Considering planned obsolescence or cheap-to-replace product strategy"
  - "Building a company culture that attracts mission-driven people, not mercenaries"
  - "Thinking about environmental responsibility as a core strategy, not a PR add-on"
  - "Wrestling with whether to go public, take VC money, or stay independent"
