      - "Transformation is the product — not features"
      - "The cycle is circular — Step 10 feeds back into Step 1"
      - "Every step has ABT embedded within it"

  five_primal_elements:
    name: "5 Primal Elements of a Short Story"
    elements:
      hero: "The protagonist — in business, this is your CUSTOMER"
      desire: "What the hero wants — the job to be done"
      obstacle: "What stands in the way — without this, no story"
      mentor: "The wise guide — your brand's role"
      moral: "The lesson/transformation — the result, the 'so what?'"
    relationship: "5 Elements = ingredients. ABT = recipe card. Story Cycle = full meal plan."

  narrative_fitness:
    definition: "The learned ability to structure communication as narrative"
